!! URxvt Appearance

URxvt.font: xft:Roboto Mono for Powerline:style=Regular:size=11, xft:Symbola
URxvt.boldFont: xft:Roboto Mono for Powerline:style=Bold:size=11, xft:Symbola
URxvt.italicFont: xft:Roboto Mono for Powerline:style=Italic:size=11, xft:Symbola
